Folder Rules:

* We need to define what we mean with a folder "Exchange"!

* Separate folders instead of one folder grouping countable items, e.g.

Instead of:
- Anlagenbetrieb, Versuche, Probenahme/

Better:
- Anlagenbetrieb/
- Versuche/
- Probenahme/

Instad of:
- Bilder_Abbildungen/

Better:
- Bilder/
- Abbildungen/

* Use the same name for the same thing

Instead of:
- Data - Workpackages/
- Data-Work packages/
- Data_work packages/

Better:
- data-by-work-package/

Instead of:
- Fact sheets/
- FactSheet/
- FactSheets/
- Factsheets/

Better:
- fact-sheets
